OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBrightest early on, with some
OL,6,Fwarm sunny spells, although cloud
OL,7,Famounts generally increasing later.
OL,8,FMainly dry, but northern parts may see
OL,9,Fisolated showers. Winds light and
OL,10,Fvariable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming overcast with a band
OL,13,Fof rain which could be heavy at times,
OL,14,Fspreading northwards across the
OL,15,Fregion. Winds generally light and
OL,16,Fvariable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
