OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FOvercast with rain and low
OL,6,Fcloud, this will slowly move eastwards
OL,7,Ftowards the coast becoming cloudy with
OL,8,Fshowers during the afternoon. Light
OL,9,Fwinds inland but breezy along the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fa settled start with isolated showers
OL,14,Flater. Tuesday and Wednesday turns
OL,15,Fmore unsettled with showers,
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy especially along
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
